(30, 'Message', 'message', '', '<p><a href="index.php/message/message-from-minister">Honorable Education Minister''s Message</a> <br /><a href="index.php/message/message-from-secretary">Honorable Education Secretary''s Message</a> <br /><a href="index.php/message/message-from-chief-engineer">Chief Engineer''s Message</a></p>', '', -2, 0, 0, 0, '2012-08-10 00:11:41', 62, '', '2012-09-05 10:52:15', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-10 00:11:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 39, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(31, 'Message from Education Minister', 'message-from-education-minister', '', '<p>Education Engineering Department has set an example that the distribution of new server machine establishments, wonderful web page development, high speed internet connections, sophisticated network sharing among the employees is unique and they would be able to utilize the devices for enhancing their skills.  <br /><br />At present decade, technology has become one of the most valuable parts and glittering and glorious parcel for delivering and receiving education much more better ways. It is very encouraging that Education Engineering Department has come up with such a brave endeavor to distribute high speed internet connections to all the employees. I am urging other educational institutions to follow the examples of Education Engineering Department  and adopt such measures so that our future institutions could combine knowledge, skills and resources with the help of technology to solve problems in real life situations.  <br /><br />Our government has made significant advancements for use of digital technology in different aspects of life, specially, education and administration. I am thanking Education Engineering Department for playing supporting role in line with government initiatives to materialize Digital Bangladesh.  <br /><br />I am urging the employees to exploit and utilize all available opportunities of EED to equip them with Digital Technology skills to be development as competent workforce of the country. I hope this brave endeavor of EED will encourage other institutions to launch this kind of initiative to help achieve the vision of Digital Bangladesh.</p>', '', -2, 0, 0, 0, '2012-08-10 00:11:56', 62, '', '2012-09-05 10:53:41', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-10 00:11:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 5, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 142, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(32, 'Message from Secretary', 'message-from-secretary', '', '<p>Education is the backbone of a nation. Without education, no nation can prosper. Keeping this spirit in mind since the independence our government has been working to free the nation from the curse of illiteracy. That is why education is a top priority sector in the socio-economic development of Bangladesh which receives highest allocation in the Annual Development Programme. Development of infrastructure i.e. Construction/Re-construction of new buildings, maintenance of existing structures, repair &amp; renovation and supply of furniture to educational institutions plays a significant role for the implementation of the Govt. Policy regarding extension/expansion of education throughout the country and Education Engineering Department is entrusted with the task of developing educational institutions providing physical facilities both at urban and rural areas. Without required physical facilities no education institution can run well and can provide education to its students well in a congenial atmosphere. In such an emergent need of construction of academic buildings, the importance of the Education Engineering Department is not only limitless but its role is also broad based. That is why, an engineering cell of early 1960’s having an Engineering Advisor as a team leader and one Executive Engineer with a very few number of supporting staff, has now expanded as Education Engineering Department with a total manpower of 1218 nos.</p>', '', -2, 0, 0, 0, '2012-08-10 00:12:52', 62, '', '2012-09-04 13:30:38', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-10 00:12:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 167, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(33, 'Message from Chief Engineer', 'message-from-chief-engineer', '', '<p>Any building developed by joining bricks one after another. As the same way software engineers of our country are developing digital technology to our land. By their softwares, paper works are converting into computerized works into soft copy. Now every employee is getting benefited by using computer.</p>\r\n<p>Presently Education Engineering Department is fulfilling the dream of one of the very important portions of developing Digital Bangladesh. So they took initiative to upgrade and update their computers and computer related works like information storage system, communication skill, file updating, etc activities. Now they can use internet within their official computers. All of them have individual official email address.</p>\r\n<p>All the computers of each rooms of each and every floors are connected each other by computer network system. So administrative and official works between all the employees have become faster. Also by establishing new server, EED has become capabilities of strong data storage system.</p>\r\n<p>I am giving thank to all the employees and developers of Eduaction Engineering Department.</p>\r\n<p>Engr. Abdullahil Azad <br /> Chief Engineer <br /> Eduactional Engineering Department <br />Dhaka, Bangladesh</p>', '', -2, 0, 0, 0, '2012-08-10 00:12:55', 62, '', '2012-09-13 22:14:58', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-10 00:12:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 370, 'robots=\nauthor='),
