so-style-unhide:no;\r\n	border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n	mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext;\r\n	mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-align: center; text-indent: -0.5in;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 20pt;">Education Engineering Department</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">CITIZEN CHARTER</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Implementation of infrastructure development of all educational institutions under Ministry of Education and any other type of works assigned by Government such as:</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">01.<span> </span>Construction of new building &amp; reconstruction/extension of existing buildings.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">02.<span> </span>Repair and maintenance of old building or any other type of structure.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">03.<span> </span>Establishment of new educational institutions.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">04.<span> </span>Design of all Architectural, Structural &amp; Sanitary drawing.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">05.<span> </span>Supply of all furniture''s and equipment.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">06.<span> </span>Planning, Programming, Monitoring and Supervision of all relevant Projects.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">07.<span> </span>Co-ordination with the donors and consultants.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">08.<span> </span>Tender processing.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">09.<span> </span>Ensure the quality of all development works.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">10.<span> </span>Matters related to administration and establishment of the Department.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 20pt;">DISTRIBUTION OF WORKS (5 Steps)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 20pt;"><span style="text-decoration: none;"> </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 20pt;">A. <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Head Office</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">01.<span> </span>Planning, programming, monitoring and overall supervision of all development projects.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">02.<span> </span>Reviewing progress of works at various levels including field.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">03.<span> </span>Matters relating to administration and establishment.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">04.<span> </span>Co-ordination and supervision of all foreign aided projects.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">05.<span> </span>Co-ordination with the donors and consultants.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">06.<span> </span>Design of all Structural and Architectural drawings.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">07.<span> </span>Approval of Tenders.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">08.<span> </span>Co-ordination with Project Directors.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">09.<span> </span>All training function.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 20pt;">B. <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Circle Office (SE Office)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">01.<span> </span>Functioning of zonal administrative works.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">02.<span> </span>Approval of Tender and Estimate on the basis of nature of work as power delegated by <span> </span>Chief Engineer.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">03.<span> </span>Decision making to overcome various problems during execution of works.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">04.<span> </span>Monitoring and supervision of development works.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">05.<span> </span>After checking and examining the various data and reports which is forwarded to the HQ. etc.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 20pt;">C. <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Zone Office(EE Office)</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">01.<span> </span>Invitation of Tender, Evaluation and recommended Tender forwarded to the<span> </span>approving <span> </span>authority for approval.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">02.<span> </span>Monitoring, supervision and taking decision to implement the works timely and properly; to <span> </span>give directions for the execution of works. <span> </span><span> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">03.<span> </span>Make payment to the contractor/supplier as DDO after verification and examination.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">04.<span> </span>Matters relating to administration and establishment within the jurisdiction</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">05.<span> </span>Data and reports received from site office will be forwarded to the Circle Office.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span> </span><strong><span style="font-size: 20pt;">D. </span></strong><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Assistant Engineer''s Office(AE Office at District level)</span></span></strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">01.<span> </span>Co-ordination and supervision of all works within the Districts. <span> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;">02.<span> </span>To implement, monitor and supervision of works as per specification,</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in;"><span> </span><span> </span>design and drawing as well as the direction of the Executive Engineer.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">03.<span> </span>To recommend bills of executed works of contractor/supplier to the Executive Engineer.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">04.<span> </span>After verification and examination the data and reports received the Assistant Engineer will <span> </span>send to the Zone office.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 20pt;">E. </span></strong><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Upazila Office(SAE Office)</span></span></strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">01.<span> </span>Co-ordination and supervision of all works entire of Upazila.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">02.<span> </span>Collection of various necessary data and convey to the Assistant Engineer.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;">03.<span> </span>To keep update records in the measurement book and to prepare bill of<span> </span>contractor/supplier <span> </span>as per executed works and to send the bill the Assistant Engineer''s office.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">04.<span> </span>Any type of works assigned by Upazila parishad.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"> </p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: SutonnyMJ;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: SutonnyMJ;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.5in;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Existing Manpower of </span>Education Engineering Department<span> </sp